                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17210830-51-off262 t17210830-51-cd263"></join> last, putting him in Fear, and taking from him a Silver Watch, value 6 l. a pair of Silver Spurs value 20 s. a Silk Handkerchief value 1 s. a Penknife, and 4 s. in Money
            </rs>. The Prosecutor deposed that he was robb'd the 7th of August about 9 at Night, <placeName id="t17210830-51-crimeloc264">within 300 Yards of Islington</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17210830-51-crimeloc264" type="placeName" value="within 300 Yards of Islington"></interp>
